{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The mimics are on the loose - find and catch them! Explore interactive handcrafted 3D dioramas and solve environmental puzzles in order to reveal the hidden mimics.\u00a0</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3395420/extras/PAM_desc.png?t=1733911919\" /><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Pesky but adorable mimics are imitating all kinds of things - if you spot one, grab it!</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Handcrafted scenes that are brimming with detail. Rotate and explore 3D dioramas to investigate every nook and cranny.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use your wits to poke, move, collect and combine objects in order to reveal the mimics and their hiding places.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A responsive environment with high quality interactions and animations.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Awesome music! Enjoy the beat while you search.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A quirky storyline with plenty of puns.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3395420/extras/mimic.png?t=1733911919\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3395420/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1733911919","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3395420/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1733911919","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3395420/09b5f9f91c21700e2da2ea31f07e184277954848/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1733911919","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3395420/09b5f9f91c21700e2da2ea31f07e184277954848/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1733911919","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Ste